I would recommend taking 127 or math 110 before 189 cuz 54/16a are more computational based and for 189 it’s essential to have a geometric understanding of what’s happening. Unless ur a genius in math and geometrical thinking I wouldn’t rush it before taking either 127/110 as a result. Hope that helps
